title: Muppet Babies DVD QUALITY 202: Piggy's Hyper-Activity Book MUPPE
description:
Muppet Babies DVD QUALITY 202: Piggy's Hyper-Activity Book

As of this writing, the 1980s animated series Muppet Babies has never officially been released on DVD in the United States.

However, four episodes were released as giveaways with plush toys in 2003.

Here is one of them, in full DVD quality for you to enjoy.


Muppet Babies
Episode 202: Piggy's Hyper-Activity Book
Air Date	 September 21, 1985
Written by	Jeffrey Scott

On a rainy day, the Babies try to build a house out of cardboard boxes, but when it fails due to Gonzo's clumsiness, they play with an activity book, and find themselves inside the activities -- connecting dots, coloring, paper dolls and more --

Song: "Music Is Everywhere"
